“We are restoring many of the cultural sites across the country, we are unveiling new ones that we are discovering as we move along. It’s an ongoing project but depending on the resources that we have. But we are grateful that we have the sports and social development fund that can give us money to keep pushing us forward,” she stressed adding that the government will not ignore any of the heritage sites saying they must be protected and preserved for the future generation. 



